Colleen Harris was found guilty of murdering Robert Edward 'Bob' Harris in their Placerville, California home in 2013 . 
  In 1985 she shot dead her second husband and the father of her three children after claiming he had been abusive to her . 
  She will be sentenced on June 5 and stands to receive 50 years to life for first-degree murder with a firearm . 
  She first testified that Bob Harris may have committed suicide . 
  But she later said that the shooting was an accident that happened when the couple wrestled over a shotgun . 
  It took the El Dorado Superior Court jury less than two hours to convict her of murder . 
 